longBusinessSummary: GSP Resource Corp. engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in Canada. It primarily explores for copper, gold, silver, molybdenum, and palladium deposits. The company has an option to acquire a 100% interest in the Alwin project covering an area of 575.72 hectares located in Logan Lake, British Columbia; and the Olivine Mountain property that consists of an area of 3021.87 hectares situated in the Similkameen Mining District of British Columbia. GSP Resource Corp. was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
